FBIS4-6011 "dreas074_c_94036" FBIS-EAS-94-074 Daily Report 12 Apr 1994 North Korea Kim Il-song Receives Flowers for Birthday Kim Il-song Receives Flowers for Birthday From PLO's 'Arafat SK1204233494 Pyongyang KCNA in English 2241 GMT 12 Apr 94 SK1204233494 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, April 12 (KCNA) -- Yasir 'Arafat, president of the State of Palestine and chairman of the Executive Committee of the Palestine Liberation Organization (PLO), sent a floral basket to President Kim Il-song of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea, on his birthday. The floral basket was handed Tuesday to an official concerned by Palestinian Ambassador to Korea Shahir Mohammed.
